## DTO Mapping Rule

DTOs belong exclusively to the Presentation Layer.

Controllers shall convert Request DTOs into Domain Models or Runtime Models before invoking the Service layer.

Likewise, Services shall convert Domain Models into Response DTOs before returning data to Controllers.

The Domain Layer and XML Engine shall never depend on DTO classes.

Mapping responsibilities belong to dedicated Mapper components.

