# 7. Design Principles

## Single Responsibility Principle

Every component shall have exactly one primary responsibility.

---

## Separation of Concerns

Presentation, business logic, persistence, and XML generation shall remain independent.

---

## Stateless Services

Services shall not maintain user session state.

Every request shall contain all information required for execution.

---

## Reusable XML Engine

The XML Generation Engine shall be independent from:

* HTTP
* Database
* UI

The Engine should be reusable from:

* REST APIs
* Batch Jobs
* CLI Tools

---

## Testability

Business logic shall be testable without requiring:

* HTTP Server
* Database
* UI

Dependency Injection is recommended for all Services and Engine components.

